Class User

java.lang.Object
users.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
Administrator, Doctor, Patient, Pharmacist
public abstract class User extends Object
The User class represents a generic user in the hospital system with basic properties such as ID, name, role, password, contact information, date of birth, and gender. This class is designed to be extended by more specific user types (e.g., Doctor, Patient).

    • User

      public User(String id, String name, String role, String password, String phoneNumber, String emailAddress, String dateOfBirth, String gender)
      Constructs a User object with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      id - the unique hospital ID for the user
      name - the full name of the user
      role - the role of the user (e.g., Patient, Doctor, etc.)
      password - the password for the user's account
      phoneNumber - the contact number of the user
      emailAddress - the email address of the user
      dateOfBirth - the date of birth of the user in the format yyyy-MM-dd
      gender - the gender of the user
